@page "/animals/lions"

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ROAR! Lions: The COOLEST Cats Ever!</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Comic+Neue:wght@400;700&family=Fredoka+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Comic Neue', cursive;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 80vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: brightness(70%);
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            text-align: center;
            color: black;
            z-index: 1;
        }

            .hero-content h1 {
                font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
                font-size: 4.5rem;
                text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #4C724C;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

            .hero-content p {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            }

        .content-section {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .text-img {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #4b5c42;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transform: perspective(1000px);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

            .text-img:hover {
                transform: scale(1.02) rotateY(5deg);
            }

        .content-text {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 30px;
        }

            .content-text h2 {
                font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
                color: white;
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

        .text-img img {
            width: 50%;
            height: 500px;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .text-img:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .video-section {
            background-color: #4a4a4a;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

            .video-section h2 {
                font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .video-section video {
                max-width: 100%;
                border-radius: 15px;
                box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            }

        .cta-section {
            background-color: #4C724C;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

            .cta-section h2 {
                font-family: 'Fredoka One', cursive;
                font-size: 3.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: white;
            color: #4C724C;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

            .cta-button:hover {
                transform: scale(1.1) rotate(3deg);
                background-color: #f0f0f0;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="hero">
        <img src="/images/lion-in-zoo.jpg" alt="Lions in the Wild" class="hero-image" />
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>ROAR! LION POWER!</h1>
            <p>Get Ready for the WILDEST Animal Adventure EVER!</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="text-img">
            <div class="content-text">
                <h2>LION SQUAD GOALS!</h2>
                <p>Lions are like the ULTIMATE FAMILY! They hang out in AWESOME groups called prides. Imagine having a whole family of SUPER COOL cats with AMAZING hair (that's their awesome mane)! 🦁</p>
            </div>
            <img src="/images/LION.jpg" alt="Lion Pride" />
        </div>

        <div class="video-section">
            <h2>LION HUNT ACTION!</h2>
            <video controls>
                <source src="/videos/lion-hunt.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>WANT TO MEET THE LION KINGS?!</h2>
        <a href="/book-options" class="cta-button">ROAR INTO ACTION!</a>
    </section>
</body>
</html>